ield]] || 2003\u20132011\n|-\n|| Hon [[Kristina Keneally]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Heffron|Heffron]] || 2003\u20132012\n|-\n|| [[Malcolm Kerr (politician)|Malcolm Kerr]] || Liberal || [[Electoral district of Cronulla|Cronulla]] || 1984\u20132011\n|-\n|| [[Ninos Khoshaba]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Smithfield|Smithfield]] || 2007\u20132011\n|-\n|| Hon [[Phil Koperberg]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Blue Mountains|Blue Mountains]] || 2007\u20132011\n|-\n|| [[Nick Lalich]] {{ref label|3|3|3}}  || Labor || [[Electoral district of Cabramatta|Cabramatta]] || 2008\u2013present\n|-\n|| Hon [[Paul Lynch (politician)|Paul Lynch]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Liverpool|Liverpool]] || 1995\u2013present\n|-\n|| [[Daryl Maguire]] || Liberal || [[Electoral district of Wagga Wagga|Wagga Wagga]] || 1999\u20132018\n|-\n|| [[Gerard Martin]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Bathurst|Bathurst]] || 1999\u20132011\n|-\n|| Hon [[Grant McBride]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of The Entrance|The Entrance]] || 1992\u20132011\n|-\n|| [[Andrew McDonald (Australian politician)|Andrew McDonald]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Macquarie Fields|Macquarie Fields]] || 2007\u20132015\n|-\n|| [[Jodi McKay]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Newcastle|Newcastle]] || 2007\u20132011\n|-\n|| [[Paul McLeay]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Heathcote|Heathcote]] || 2003\u20132011\n|-\n|| [[Lylea McMahon]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Shellharbour|Shellharbour]] || 2007\u20132011\n|-\n|| Hon [[Reba Meagher]] {{ref label|3|3|3}}  || Labor || [[Electoral district of Cabramatta|Cabramatta]] || 1994\u20132008\n|-\n|| [[Alison Megarrity]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Menai|Menai]] || 1999\u20132011\n|-\n|| [[Wayne Merton]] || Liberal || [[Electoral district of Baulkham Hills|Baulkham Hills]] || 1988\u20132011\n|-\n|| [[Matthew Morris (politician)|Matthew Morris]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Charlestown|Charlestown]] || 2003\u20132011\n|-\n|