ropology of the Knowing Subject |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sGCBQPZMyqIC |year=2012 |publisher=[[University of Chicago Press]] |isbn=978-0-226-52226-5}}\n* {{cite book |last1=Okuda |first1=Michael |authorlink1=Michael Okuda |last2=Okuda |first2=Denise |authorlink2=Denise Okuda |year=1999 |title=The Star Trek Encyclopedia: A Reference Guide to the Future |publisher=Pocket Books |isbn=978-0-671-53609-1 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VOeZQhAQZHgC |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Pickover |first=Clifford A. |authorlink1=Clifford A. Pickover |year=2008 |title=Archimedes to Hawking: laws of science and the great minds behind them |publisher=Oxford University Press |isbn=978-0-19-533611-5 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SQXcpvjcJBUC |access-date=4 March 2012}}\n* {{cite book |last1=White |first1=Michael |last2=Gribbin |first2=John |year=2002 |title=Stephen Hawking: A Life in Science |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NoE6FAnDtRYC |edition=2nd |publisher=National Academies Press |isbn=978-0-309-08410-9 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Yulsman |first=Tom |title=Origins: the quest for our cosmic roots |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=eh3_GfqlDlMC |year=2003 |publisher=CRC Press |isbn=978-0-7503-0765-9 |ref=harv}}\n\n{{refend}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{sister project links|wikt=Hawking|n=Category:Stephen Hawking|v=no|s=no|b=General Astronomy/Black Holes in Hiding}}\n{{Library resources box|by=yes|about=yes}}\n{{Portal|Physics}}\n* {{Official website|http://www.hawking.org.uk/}}\n* {{facebook|stephenhawking}}\n* {{IMDb name|370071}}\n* {{In Our Time|Professor Stephen Hawking Collection|p06132wb|Stephen Hawking}}\n* {{isfdb name|37485}}\n* {{NPG name|name=Stephen William Hawking}}\n* {{UK National Archives ID}}\n* {{GoogleScholar|id=qj74uXkAAAAJ}}\n* {{NYTtopic|people/h/stephen_w_hawking}}\n* {{Scopus|id= 6701475619}}\n* {{Britannica|257505}}\n* {{MacTutor|id=Hawking}}\n* {{C-SPAN|stephenhawking}}\n* {{Worldcat id|lccn-n81-20731}}\n* {{Guardian topic}}\n* {{TED speaker}}\n* {{cite web |url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/mg21328460-500-stephen-hawking-at-70-exclusive-interview/ |title=Stephen Hawking at 70: Exclusive interview |newspaper=[[New Scientist]] |date=4 January 2012}}\n* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TdjAJeUy0zM The Universe and Beyond, with Stephen Hawking] StarTalk video\n* {{youtube|4AW9GoUeaPE|Stephen Hawking's Black Hole Theory (video; 08:39; 16 October 2018)}} ([https://www.newscientist.com/article/mg24032002-000-sneak-peek-at-hawkings-last-book-brief-answers-to-the-big-questions/ text])\n* [http://www.bbc.com/earth/story/20160107-these-are-the-discoveries-that-made-stephen-hawking-famous These Are The Discoveries that made Stephen Hawking Famous], by Phillip Ball.\n\n{{Stephen Hawking}}\n{{Template group\n|title = Articles related to Stephen Hawking\n|list =\n{{Lucasian Professors of Mathematics}}\n{{Copley Medallists 2001\u20132050}}\n{{FRS 1974}}\n{{Breakthrough Prize laureates}}\n{{Wolf Prize in Physics}}\n{{Prince of Asturias Award for Concord}}\n{{Existential risk from artificial intelligence}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Hawking, Stephen}}\n[[Category:Stephen Hawking|Stephen Hawking]]\n[[Category:1942 births]]\n[[Category:2018 deaths]]\n[[Category:20th-century atheists]]\n[[Category:20th-century astronomers]]\n[[Category:21st-century astronomers]]\n[[Category:20th-century English writers]]\n[[Category:21st-century atheists]]\n[[Category:21st-century English writers]]\n[[Category:Academics of the University of Cambridge]]\n[[Category:Albert Einstein Medal recipients]]\n[[Category:Alumni of Trinity Hall, Cambridge]]\n[[Category:Alumni of University College, Oxford]]\n[[Category:Anti\u2013Iraq War activists]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:British transhumanists]]\n[[Category:Burials at Westminster Abbey]]\n[[Category:Commanders of the Order of the British Empire]]\n[[Category:Cosmologists]]\n[[Category:Deaths from motor neuron dise